= SDL_HapticStopAll =
Use this function to stop all the currently playing effects on a haptic device.


== Syntax ==
```c++
int SDL_HapticStopAll(SDL_Haptic* haptic)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''haptic'''
|^a pointer to the^ haptic device to stop
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns 0 on success, or -1 on failure; call [[SDL_GetError]]() for more information.

